Name: LANDING
checklistText:
1. Emer Drogue Fuse 				- ON (BEFORE 30,000 FT)
2. At 21,000 ft. check drogue chute deployment
3. At appx. 20,000ft, Snorkel Ring 	- PULL
4. Emer O2 handle 					- EMER
5. Landing Bag switch 				- AUTO
6. Main light illuminates green at 10,000 ft
7. UHF/DF switch 					- R/T
8. Press Reg Handle 				- PULL
9. Check "Landing Bag" Telelight 	- GREEN
10. "Fuel Quan" warning light		- ILLUMINATED
After Impact:
1. ASCS AC Bus switch 				- OFF
2. Photo Lights switch 				- OFF
